author: Caitlyn Gribbin
title: Essential fruit and veg pickers 'homeless', meaning crops may be left to rot
description: With nowhere for working backpackers to stay as hostels and caravan parks close due to coronavirus, there are warnings about the supply of winter fruit and vegetables in the coming months.
content:
Posted 
April 09, 2020 06:42:29
The fruit and vegetable industry has warned that crops may be left to rot in fields because of a major shortage of accommodation for backpackers who pick the produce.
